| Comment: DNS Tunneling - Potential Data Exfiltration
| Comment: Detects abnormally long DNS queries that may indicate DNS tunneling for data exfiltration
| Comment: MITRE ATT&CK Tags: attack.exfiltration, attack.t1048.001, attack.command_and_control, attack.t1071.004
index=dns sourcetype=WinEventLog:Security
| search (QueryName=">= 50") OR ((QueryName="*.windows.com" OR QueryName="*.microsoft.com" OR QueryName="*.windowsupdate.com"))
| table _time, host, user, CommandLine, Image, EventID
| sort -_time